&lt;p&gt;Trauma and Orthopaedic Band 5 Nurse&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Do you like to be challenged, provide quality care, work within a dedicated Multi-disciplinary team? Then Trauma and Orthopaedics at Basildon is the place for you.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The service consists of two emergency 28 bed trauma wards and a 22 bed elective joint unit. The job offers a variety of trauma cases, rehabilitation and complex discharging. An Induction package is offered and the opportunity to undertake specialist orthopaedic courses. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
